Very insightful class for professionals working in the social services. Course touches on many aspects of our social policy from nutritional assistance to retirement. Course design is very easy to follow and ideal for those with full-time jobs or seeking to take additional classes in their free-time. I would highly recommend this course for anyone that works with the public through a governmental agency or a non-profit!
